en=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xrw1665702585620.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xrw1665702585620.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xrw1665702585620.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xrw1665702585620\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Description </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode\n      characters. </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__section_w707ab1b5b1_w708ab1b5_w709ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__table_d10859e1_d10860e1_d10861e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Physical Name: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> UDESCR </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Expected Value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> String of up to 256 characters. Supports\n                        Unicode. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Default Value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> None </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__section_pgm_pg3_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820098e94\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__p_d97043e1_d97044e1_d97045e1\">Provide a description of the object, especially if the\n            name does not provide a clear meaning. For more extensive documentation about the\n            object, use the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Documentation</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Comment</span>\n            property (if available).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__p_d97046e1_d97047e1_d97048e1\">This description is used when searching and filtering\n            objects in the IDE, so it is worthwhile providing a meaningful description to improve\n            success when trying to find objects in a large development Repository.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__section_ekh_qg3_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820098e112\">Signature Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__p_d97052e1_d97053e1_d97054e1\">Signatures of Uniface components use the description\n            defined in the component definition, but you can provide a description for non-Uniface\n            components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__p_d97055e1_d97056e1_d97057e1\">If you have previously compiled the corresponding\n            component, and the signature description is empty, the component description appears in\n            this field.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__p_d97058e1_d97059e1_d97060e1\">A keyword description can be up to 64 characters,\n            including (A-Z), numbers (0-9), and underscore (_) characters.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__section_mfv_rg3_nwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d820098e127\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__ul_djz_sg3_nwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xrw1665702585620__li_d39428e1_d39429e1_d39430e1\">All development objects </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Documentation</a><p>Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617029\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617029\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Description Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Description Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters. Physical Name: UDESCR Expected Value: String of up to 256 characters. Supports Unicode. Default Value: None Description Provide a description of the object, especially if the name does not provide a clear meaning. For more extensive documentation about the object, use the Documentation or Comment property (if available). This description is used when searching and filtering objects in the IDE, so it is worthwhile providing a meaningful description to improve success when trying to find objects in a large development Repository. Signature Description Signatures of Uniface components use the description defined in the component definition, but you can provide a description for non-Uniface components. If you have previously compiled the corresponding component, and the signature description is empty, the component description appears in this field. A keyword description can be up to 64 characters, including (A-Z), numbers (0-9), and underscore (_) characters. Applies To All development objects Related Links Documentation Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}